{
  "stem": "19982.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But he was-- he was in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he-- somehow, he, he was able to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we went to-- for a few days, we traveled to, to my town-- to Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I came to Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I walked in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "During the war, the Gestapo lived in our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "After the war, the-- it's the [NON-ENGLISH], which would have been the president, whichever, like mayor or, or, or mayor-- deputy mayor lived in our house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "When I walked in, everything was the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Only the people [SOBBING] weren't there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Even the painting on the wall was the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I fainted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And she knew right away who I am because our town was a small town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they knew my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And everybody knew that I was sent away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So she knew right away who I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then-- and then I-- the business took over-- also a Polack who-- named [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I went to him to the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They got all very uneasy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Then I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I remember I went to our super.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So he, he, himself, he came, and he says, oh, [NON-ENGLISH] is back, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And, and she just closed the door in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "She wouldn't even let me go in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There was there a family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "There what about four families in Dabrowa which stayed-- they stayed in Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I was with a Jewish family which survived, or they were hidden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I was with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then came one Polack, the one which was hiding all those people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And, and they said, you better leave because they're going to kill you here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And 4 o'clock at night, we hired a car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "This time were cars already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I went back to Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
